  <summary date="2021-06-07T19:20:13Z" status="Introduced in Senate">CARES Windfall for the Wealthiest Repeal Act

This bill restores and makes permanent the limitation on excess businesses losses of noncorporate taxpayers. It also allows taxpayers a carryback of their net operating losses arising in 2019 and 2020.</summary>
